name: DreamJourney 2.5
description:
This model is a merge of Dreamlike diffusion and Openjourney. To which were added a bit of Dreamlike Photorealism and then a bit of Protogen Anime. (There MIGHT be a small part of some other model but i'm not sure This is for the most part a pretty good general purpose model, i've been using it for a while now, it's quite good for digital paintings (too good for my taste) Works best at the following resolutions : -640x640 -768x768 -768x512 and 512x768

Ps : I put commercial use to none because i'm not sure of the licenses for the model that i merged also, i don't know how merges affects licensing.
